Hi Starbucks Singapore, I’ve gotten a vanilla latte and caramel mac, both hot today at Kampung Admiralty at around 6.45pm. Both drinks were Super disappointing. Vanilla latte doesn’t have vanilla taste, taste not sweet too & same goes for the caramel mac, no caramel taste except for the caramel drizzle on top... On Top of that at one moment I saw the barista taking some hot water and pour it into my caramel mac.. don’t think recipe contains water as part of the ingredients? Wasn’t the first time I experience bad coffees at this particular outlet. kudos to the cashier that managed to help me get toffee nut frap tho & her warm smile.
